These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, black, amber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, badminton, ice-hockey, rugby
4 different games are played: poker, monopoly, scrabble, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, collecting, camping
City: nizza, new-york, paris, miami
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person playing chess is between the person who likes blue and the person traveling to miami##2
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who likes blue and the person playing scrabble##2
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Color           | black | blue   | amber | blood-red |
| Sport   | cricket      | badminton | ice-hockey              | rugby |
| Game   | poker       | monopoly     | chess               | scrabble    |
| Hobby           | cooking        | collecting     | camping           | traveling       |
| City     | new-york | paris     | nizza                | miami      |

