The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, september, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, davidoff, ritmeester, cain
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the nigerian##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the italian and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the person driving the ship is the havana-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the havana-smoker is the italian##1
12. the dutch is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Nationality          | italian       | nigerian      | dutch      | british      |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | drawing | collecting | woodworking |
