 3. the wooden house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person playing snooker is the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the modern house is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's birthday is in may and the ranch-style house##2
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
11. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
