 1. the french is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the owner of the snake is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person playing chess##2
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the bongani-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##2
 4. the person playing scrabble is the russian##1
 5. the owner of the frog is the dutch##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the owner of the hedgehog is between the dutch and the person playing monopoly##2
12. the owner of the snake is between the person playing scrabble and the davidoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | dannemann      | davidoff         | bongani | tiparillo      |
| Nationality           | dutch | brazilian | french | russian     |
| Hobby   | hiking         | collecting          | rock-climbing  | reading |
| Pet         | frog        | hedgehog  | snake | dog   |
| Game     | go    | chess         | monopoly     | scrabble     |

