.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, nigerian, brazilian, canadian
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, dancing, rock-climbing
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, light-blue, chestnut, mauve
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, mirinda, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, funk, soul, folk
 1. the person who likes mauve is between the person drinking mirinda and the fan funk##2
 2. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the fan soul##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the nigerian##1
 7. the russian is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan metal##1
11. the canadian is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
