.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
House: tower, modern, craftsman, futuristic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake, rabbit
There 4 different types of food: orange, tomato, cucumber, apricot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, august, december
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, canasta, whist
 1. the person eating cucumber is the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 3. the modern house is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person eating apricot##2
 4. the person eating apricot is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the tower house is between the modern house and the person playing whist##2
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the modern house is on the right of the person eating orange##1
10. the craftsman house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
