.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, nurse, software-developer, photographer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, bellflower, iris
House: wooden, cottage, cape-cod, ranch-style
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, snooker, monopoly
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, azure, fuchsia
 1. the person who growsiris is the cottage house##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is between the ranch-style house and the person playing whist##2
 3. the person who likes chestnut is between the person playing bridge and the person who likes azure##2
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the photographer##1
 7. the nurse is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
10. the police-officer is the wooden house##1
11. the wooden house is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job         | software-developer  | nurse | photographer | police-officer |
| Flower   | iris      | azalea   | bellflower      | dahlia    |
| House   | cottage  | cape-cod | ranch-style        | wooden     |
| Game         | whist  | bridge  | snooker     | monopoly      |
| Color     | aquamarine | fuchsia      | chestnut   | azure       |

 